  ${
    $d a b c e m K $.
    grpprop.b $e |- ( Base ` K ) = ( Base ` L ) $.
    grpprop.p $e |- ( +g ` K ) = ( +g ` L ) $.
    $( If two structures have the same group components (properties), one is a
       group iff the other one is. $)
    grpprop $p |- ( K e. Grp <-> L e. Grp ) $=
      ( va vb vc ve vm cgrp wcel cv cplusg cfv co cbs wceq wa wral wrex eqid
      isgrp2 bitr4i ) AJKELZFLZAMNZOZAPNZKUGGLZUFOUDUEUIUFOUFOQRGUHSFUHSEUHSHLZ
      UDUFOUDQILUDUFOUJQIUHTREUHSHUHTRBJKUHUFHIAEFGUHUAUFUAUBUHUFHIBEFGCDUBUC
      $.
